| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3373 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d7a67a73-5af0-56dd-b0d9-dcc2b3aa6cac"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
